high_descs: Walk across room to the counter top that the toaster is on.
Pick up the fork on the right side of the toaster.
Move across room to the dishwasher.
On the counter above the dishwasher there is a round pan.  Pick up the pan.
Put the fork in the pan and turn around.
Go back to the sink with carrying the pan and the fork.
Place the fork and the pan in the bottom of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Putting dirty dishes in the sink.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk towards the counter with the paper towels, then turn left and walk to the counter to the nearest right of the stove.
Pick up the fork from the counter.
Turn around and walk towards the sink on the left.
Pick up the pan above the dishwasher.
Put away the fork.
Pick up the fork and pan on the counter and turn left towards the sink.
Place the fork and the pan in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the dirty utensils in the sink.

high_descs: Go to the kitchen counter on the right of the stove.
Pick up the fork behind the spoon.
Turn around to go to  the frying pan on the right of the sink.
Place the fork in the frying pan.
Pick up the frying pan with the fork in it.
Go left to the front of the sink.
Place the frying pan and the fork in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the pan with a fork in the sink.

high_descs: Right and forward across the kitchen to the counter right of the oven
Pick up the fork right of the toaster from the counter
Turn right and walk a few feet to the counter right of the sink
Put the fork in the round pan on the counter
Pick up the pan from the counter
Turn left and face toward the sink
Put the pan into the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the pan with fork in the kitchen sink

high_descs: Head towards the toaster oven sitting on top of the kitchen cabinet.
Grab the fork next to the toaster oven.
Turn around and head towards the pan sitting on top of the kitchen cabinet to the right of the sink.
Place the fork in the pan.
Grab the pan containing the fork.
Head towards the front of the sink on the left.
Place the pan and fork into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Fetch a pan and fork and place them in the sink.

high_descs: Head ahead and to the right and face the toaster on the counter.
Pick up the fork to the right of the toaster.
Turn around and walk a few steps to the right of the sink.
Put the fork in the pan to the right of the sink.
Pick up the stack of items.
Take a step left and face the sink.
Put the items in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a fork resting in a pan in the sink.
